\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 15/7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 15/7.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191252.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I VS NAM \u0110\u1ecaNH</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4236","checkdouble":"191252"},{"date":"09:54 15/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/diem-nhan-sau-tran-hagl-31-can-tho-cong-dau-cua-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</h2><h2>1. M\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL sau pha b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n S\u01a1n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00f4 V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecfng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong 45 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/anh3_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt ph\u00fat, V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi sau pha d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhanh b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 v\u00e0o trong cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 trong 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng cho HAGL. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh hay tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t vui cho HAGL trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 3 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ngo\u1ea1i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar Francisco ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Osmar ghi b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng x\u00f3a tan \u0111i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i SLNA. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, Osmar nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/aGFnbF9jb25ncGh1b25nX2FubXVuZw==.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp nhanh c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi m\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Osmar, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Zeba Josip, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a HAGL. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo k\u00e8m ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Patiyo. Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HAGL th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1 khi b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng Vissai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 HAGL v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 61 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ngo\u1ea1i binh Wander Luiz b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. B\u00f3ng \u0111i hi\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u01a1i cao so v\u1edbi x\u00e0 ngang HAGL. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 Patiyo lao\u00a0v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o th\u00eam r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n x\u00f4 x\u00e1t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Quang T\u00ecnh b\u00ean ph\u00eda C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 pha tranh b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau v\u1edbi Quang T\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, khi\u1ebfn Quang T\u00ecnh b\u1ecb ng\u00e3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o ng\u1ef1c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 779px;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 777px;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 769px;\"><img alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/cp-quangtinh.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat CLB HA Gia Lai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba khi \u0111\u1ecbnh lao v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. R\u1ea5t may sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp can ng\u0103n hai c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng. C\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Quang T\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng hay v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng n\u1eefa, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 1 tr\u1eadn. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.</p>\r\n<h2>5. C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1ee5t s\u00e2u tr\u00ean BXH<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 19\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/BXH-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4235","checkdouble":"191237"},{"date":"10:04 15/07","title":"Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos. Los Blancos v\u1eeba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Modric \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 Kovacic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u1ede Anh, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, bao g\u1ed3m MU, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU nh\u1eafm Kovacic thay th\u1ebf Carrick</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia thay th\u1ebf cho Dembele, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Man xanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau\u00a0m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" title=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Kovacic t\u1eeb Inter Milan, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, Kovacic s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 \u1edf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng xong. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4234","checkdouble":"191234"},{"date":"10:41 15/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh r\u1ea5t vui khi CR7 ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3 Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Donbalon th\u00ec l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Bale \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Isco v\u00e0 Asensio, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN v\u00e0 gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Real \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Gareth Bale lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Daily Mail, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Bale tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-giam-gia-ban-gareth-bale-cho-mu-172-184790.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Bale</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4233","checkdouble":"191238"}]}